Package: perfsmooth
Type: Package
Title: Fit smooth, monotonic curve to performance data
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Robert",
           family = "Link",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "ard"),
           email = "rl8z@virginia.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7071-248X"))
Description: Given a set of empirical estimates of an algorithm's performance
    (e.g., something like positive predictive value) as a function of some measure
    of sensitivity, estimate a performance curve that enforces the constraint
    that performance decreases as sensitivity decreases.
